ActCanadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission Act
PrecisRe-appointment of JOANNE T. LEVY of Warman, Saskatchewan, as a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and her designation for the Manitoba/Saskatchewan region, effective July 3, 2023.
